<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; background: #f8f9fa; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background: #22C55E; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 10px 5px; }
    .button.decline { background: #EF4444; }
    .document-preview { background: white; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin: 15px 0; font-family: monospace; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üìÑ Review Your Business Registration Documents</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>
      
      <p>Your incorporation documents for <strong><%= @registration.business_name %></strong> are ready for review!</p>
      
      <div class="document-preview">
        <h3>Document Preview:</h3>
        <pre><%= truncate(@document.generated_content, length: 500) %></pre>
        <p><em>...and more</em></p>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Registration Details:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Business Name: <%= @registration.business_name %></li>
        <li>Business Type: <%= @registration.business_category.name %></li>
        <li>State: <%= @registration.state.name %></li>
        <li>Total Cost: <%= @registration.formatted_fees %></li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Please review the document carefully. If everything looks correct, click "Approve" to proceed with e-signature and payment. If you need changes, click "Request Changes".</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= @approval_url %>" class="button">‚úÖ Approve Document</a>
        <a href="<%= @decline_url %>" class="button decline">‚ùå Request Changes</a>
      </div>
      
      <p><small>This approval link expires in 7 days. If you have questions, contact our support team.</small></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>